    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Galaxy Kingdoms</strong> is an action/adventure shooter. Feel the journey of a bounty hunter as he explores the galaxy in search of quests and treasure. Strengthen yourself by buying new weapons and armor and then take on more powerful enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle For Rewards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free to choose how you will face your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies are intelligent, so the louder the noise, the more unwanted attention you will attract!Choose the best combat mode to complete the mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are not afraid to die, fight with everything!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/3a6788384b41620a8ba07e757559f439.poster.avif?t=1756125586\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/3a6788384b41620a8ba07e757559f439.webm?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/3a6788384b41620a8ba07e757559f439.mp4?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or be cautious and fight in the shadows.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/3423e1d94b548a7fe7af5a09026776f3.poster.avif?t=1756125586\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/3423e1d94b548a7fe7af5a09026776f3.webm?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/3423e1d94b548a7fe7af5a09026776f3.mp4?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buy New Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons will not be lacking! You will find a huge variety of weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/5d0d36ddaf00c4757a8d14d2954a57e2.poster.avif?t=1756125586\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/5d0d36ddaf00c4757a8d14d2954a57e2.webm?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/5d0d36ddaf00c4757a8d14d2954a57e2.mp4?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For each mission there is an ideal weapon, so choose your weapon wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/8028d05f6f57f8f927410b8b0412d312.poster.avif?t=1756125586\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/8028d05f6f57f8f927410b8b0412d312.webm?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/8028d05f6f57f8f927410b8b0412d312.mp4?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Melhore Suas Armas!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to be a famous and feared bounty hunter, you will need very strong weapons, so you need to upgrade your weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/1a72a1a3d39352ea16cb81038c4d2de9.poster.avif?t=1756125586\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/1a72a1a3d39352ea16cb81038c4d2de9.webm?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206230/extras/1a72a1a3d39352ea16cb81038c4d2de9.mp4?t=1756125586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accept missions to get rewards.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different planets in search of treasure.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy various weapons and upgrade them</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy various armors</p></li></ul>",
